title: 10 Best Windows Utilities From Nirsoft
tags: 15 NirSoft Utilities Every Windows User Should Have
description:
Nirsoft has made some of the best apps for Windows and in this video, we have picked our top 10 utilities from Nirsoft. 

Download Nirlaucher from here -- 
http://launcher.nirsoft.net/


[List of Apps used in the video]


#1 ProduKey -- find the product key
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/product_cd_key_viewer.html

#2 CurrPorts
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/cports.html

#3 ChromeCacheView -- See Images Store in the Browser Cache 
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/chrome_cache_view.html

#4 VideoCacheView -- Find Videos Store in the Browser Cache 
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/video_cache_view.html

#5 HostedNetworkStarter -- Create WiFi hotspot
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/wifi_hotspot_starter.html

#6 QuickSetDNS -- Change DNS server with one click
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/quick_set_dns.html

#7 FolderChangesView
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/folder_changes_view.html

#8 Wireless Key Viewer -- find all the saved WiFi password
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/wireless_key.html

#9 WebBrowserPassView --  Recover password saved in browser. 
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/web_browser_password.html

#10 Wireless Network watcher -- find the devices on your network
http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/wireless_network_watcher.html
